#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/11_The_Court_of_Karrag.cfg:144
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/11_The_Court_of_Karrag.cfg:153
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/12_The_Underlevels.cfg:60
